                                <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.2">
                                    <locus from="12r" to="20r"/>
                                    <title type="complete">List of the successors of <persName ref="PRS10303Yekunno"/> and summaries of the events of their reigns, 
                                        until the death of <persName ref="PRS6229LebnaDe"/>
                                    </title>
                                    <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                                    <note>
                                        The following is the list of the successors of <persName ref="PRS10303Yekunno"/>:
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS10303Yekunno"/> reigned for 15 years. </p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS10215Yagbas" xml:lang="gez">ያግብአ፡ ጽዮን፡</persName> reigned for nine years.</p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS5326hezbaAs" xml:lang="gez">ሕዝበ፡ አስገድ፡</persName>, <persName ref="PRS8029QedmaAs">ቅድመ፡ አስገድ፡</persName>,
                                            <persName ref="PRS8757senfaAr" xml:lang="gez">ጽንፈ፡ አርዓድ፡</persName> and their two brothers reigned for five years. </p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS10111WedemR" xml:lang="gez">ውድም፡ አርዓድ፡</persName> reigned for 15 years.</p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS1854Amdase" xml:lang="gez">ዓምደ፡ ጽዮን፡</persName> reigned for thirty years. 
                                            <q xml:lang="en">He was suddenly attacked by ten kings at a time when he had not assembled his army. He fought and defeated them. <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe"/>
                                            </q>
                                        </p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS8595SayfaAr" xml:lang="gez">ሰይፈ፡ አርዓድ፡</persName> reigned for 28 years.</p>
                                        <p>   His son <persName ref="PRS7559NewayaM" xml:lang="gez">ውድም፡ አስፈሬ፡</persName> reigned for ten years.</p>
                                        <p> 
                                            <persName ref="PRS3429DawitII"/> reigned for 29 years. 
                                            <q xml:lang="en">Under his reign the glorious cross of Our Lord Jesus Christ
                                                appeared, which caused miracles before hima and his troups <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe"/>
                                            </q>
                                            <q xml:lang="gez">ውእቱኒ፡ ተመጠዎ፡ በክብር፡ ወበሥርዓተ፡ መንግሥት።</q>
                                        </p>
                                        <p> 
                                            <persName ref="PRS9429Tewodros"/> reigned for three years. </p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS10342Yeshaq"/> reigned for 15 years. 
                                            <q xml:lang="en">In the tenth year of his reign the 13th cycle came to an end.
                                                From <persName ref="PRS10303Yekunno"/> until this time, 54 years had elapsed, and altogether <supplied reason="explanation" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">since creation</supplied> 6917 years.</q>
                                        </p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS3790endreyas" xml:lang="gez">እንድርያስ፡</persName>, the son of <persName ref="PRS10342Yeshaq"/> reigned for six months.</p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS9175TaklaMa" xml:lang="gez">ሕዝበ፡ ናኝ፡</persName> and <persName ref="PRS1843AmdaIy" xml:lang="gez">ዓምደ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ በድል፡ ናኝ፡</persName> reigned for five years.</p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS10626ZaraY" xml:lang="gez">ዘርአ፡ ያዕቆብ፡</persName> reigned for 34 years and two months. 
                                            <q xml:lang="en">Under his reign there was a controversy about religion:
                                                
                                                <persName ref="PRS4709Giyorgis">
                                                    <roleName type="title">ʾabbā</roleName>
                                                </persName> 
                                                <persName ref="PRS4709Giyorgis"/>
                                                had a discussion with a European and then wrote 
                                                <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1952Mashaf"/>. Furthermore, a heathen from the land of <placeName ref="LOC1095Adal"/> called
                                                <persName ref="PRS11953Badlay" xml:lang="gez">በድላይ፡</persName>, who completely ressembled <persName ref="PRS11293Goliath"/> the Philistine,
                                                came to fight him. He <supplied reason="explanation" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">the king</supplied> defeated him,
                                                killed him and obtained all his possessions. By the power of his allmighty God he let no enemy
                                                survive.
                                            </q>
                                        </p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS2334BaedaM" xml:lang="gez">በእደ፡ ማርያም፡</persName>
                                            <q xml:lang="gez">ወሥዕሉኒ፡ ሀለወ፡ በአቶሮንሰ፡ ማርያም፡</q>
                                        </p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS3874eskender" xml:lang="gez">እስክንድር፡</persName>
                                        </p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS7481NaodA" xml:lang="gez">ናዖድ፡</persName>
                                        </p>
                                        <p>
                                            <persName ref="PRS6229LebnaDe" xml:lang="gez">ወናግ፡ ሰገድ፡</persName>
                                        </p>
                                    </note>
